dialogue: Wally, this is my brother, Phil, the prince of insufficient light.
I asked him to interpret your accomplishments for this quarter.
Eight of these accomplishments involved simply being on a project team that did something.
Nine accomplishments involved fixing problems you created.
Five of these are just buzzwords that don't mean anything.
And three are duplicates that you reworded to appear different.
I'd recommend harvesting his organs, but those probably don't work either.
